title: Flight Simulator 2020 - POI's - Germany -  Rheinsberg Palace
description:
In this video we will fly over the Rheinsberg Palace . Rheinsberg Palace (German: Schloss Rheinsberg) lies in the municipality of Rheinsberg, about 100 kilometres (62 mi) northwest of Berlin in the German district of Ostprignitz-Ruppin.

The palace on the eastern shore of the Grienericksee [de] is a classic example of the so-called Frederician Rococo architecture style and served as a basis for Sanssouci Palace.
